ActAn Act to Implement Conventions for the Avoidance of Double Taxation with respect to Income Tax between Canada and France, Canada and Belgium and Canada and Israel
SubjectAgreement between Canada and the French Republic for the Avoidance of Double Taxation and the Prevention of Fiscal Evasion
PrecisOrder directing that a proclamation do issue giving notice of the ENTRY INTO FORCE, on December 27, 2013 of the February 2, 2010 supplementary agreement of the Protocole amending the CONVENTION between the Government of Canada and the Government of the FRENCH REPUBLIC for the AVOIDANCE OF DOUBLE TAXATION AND THE PREVENTION OF FISCAL EVASION WITH RESPECT TO TAXES ON INCOME AND ON CAPITAL signed on May 2, 1975, as amended by the Protocol signed on January 16, 1987 and as further amended by the Protocol signed on November 30, 1995.
